url_conventions.description:
In-content URL formats for cross-referencing:

App protocol (stored in backend):
- resource://  {resourceId}
- tasks://     {taskId}
- note://      {taskId}/{noteId}

Local file paths (in sync folder):
- ./resources/{resourceId}.{ext}
- ./{Task-Title}.md
- ./{TaskTitle}-{NoteFirstLine}.md

Clients convert between formats during sync.
